Medievalist's Quest

Cein Chavez

You open the door to your home, and with a tiresome push of your hand, you close the door. Famished from your exploration of the light woods outside you decide to treat yourself to some popped corn.

The room you stand in is... Well, the only room in your house which is your living room (Yes this is a 1 room house don't judge) This cozy upper floor has all your living necessities such as a cooking place, a table, firewood for the cooking place, and some nice vases which stand on a shelf above the firewood, and the basement. Pretty scary down there you don't really go often.

>Begin Adventure

> Living Quarters
>Begin Adventure

Well before you begin you might as well introduce yourself to... Yourself I guess.
Your name is Jonathan. You're a mighty warrior! (well in your mind you are) and you love to adventure it's pretty much a passion at this point. I mean you don't get paid but it's fun to do. You live by yourself in the outskirts of these woods that you humbly called the "Light woods" because it's not as thick as a normal forest is. Hmm... You also like fighting, Yes! You wish you can become as powerful as other mighty warriors you know, but a man can dream.

Stats
HP~ 100
Vigor~10
Creativity~15
Spunk~30

Now that THAT'S over we can finally satisfy our hunger with popped corn!
