Ah, the good old cooking pit. The place where you usually cook all of your meals that you get on your travels. The only travel you went on to get this was to the table which is at the southernmost part of the house, and might you add it was treacherous! Well, you won't be able to light this fire unless you have some kind of fire making tool.

